name: Badrinath Ki Dulhania
review:
Very nice in parts with good funny dialogues. But mostly weak in quality and script writing. Sahil Vaid and Alia Bhatt delivered a superb performance where Varun Dhawan was decent. Shashank Khaitan should experiment and attempt more, without sticking himself to Dulhania series. Songs were average and just mildly gelled with the movie flow.
